Trierweiler says it is unlikely she will return to her career as a political journalist as covering stories about Hollande would be too complicated.

She instead plans to launch a career as a humanitarian campaigner.

Meanwhile, the Socialist president’s staff have now completely eradicated some 130 images of Ms Trierweiler from the official Elysee website, along with all other references to her.

Mr Hollande, who has never married, is now expected to remain a ‘bachelor president’ for a while, while continuing with his relationship with Ms Gayet outside the Elysee.

